  <brief_title>Single-Incision Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy Versus Traditional Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single-Incision Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy Versus Traditional Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy: A Randomized Prospective Trial</official_title>
